event.title: .NET Rocks Podcast
event.metaDesc: .NET Rocks! is a weekly talk show for anyone interested in programming on the Microsoft .NET platform. Hosted by Richard Campbell and Carl Franklin with guest Damian Brady.
event.content:
.NET Rocks! is a weekly talk show for anyone interested in programming on the Microsoft .NET platform.

Hosted by Richard Campbell and Carl Franklin with guests Martin Woodward and Immo Landwerth.
